877f28a935f0a7bddf63b0928873bfa2fe","tid":372871,"uid":35737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:18:13.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9daf19946d34ca78c6994425b23fec6bcb114035","tid":372871,"uid":135860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:25:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又唔見band歌melody 悶<br />\n廢就廢啦</blockquote><br />\n因為band歌的chord progression 好少用咁多大路流行曲的format 所以melody取向係唔同<br />\nBand ge作歌方式好多都係 先夾個底 再填melody <br />\n夾底的時候會考慮chord progression 悶唔悶<br />\n<br />\n作曲人作曲多數 手彈口唱 同步進行 or用大路的chord progression 改其一兩個chord 令感覺無咁悶<br />\n<br />\n而且band ge 編曲係激情豐富d 好易會有錯覺係melody好<br />\n<br />\n如 長相斯守 個melody根本係大路流行曲<br />\n但我唔否認佢地有好melody <br />\n因為佢地係band 面對的壓力同普通作曲人唔同"},{"pid":"47a5896eb7cbb8fc4f61d74859222ddb2a4129be","tid":372871,"uid":135860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:26:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打左咁多野無人理 好慘咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班韓畜推撚沉個post緊係冇人理啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都好中意k pop但唔中意唱跳<br />\n唔好block我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29003d065d1e22a4579be04eb8baf162e9204c8a","tid":372871,"uid":135860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:28:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廣東歌係好難填詞<br />\n黎黎去去都係果幾隻字開頭同埋尾，攪到好悶</blockquote><br />\n岩呀 精妙的用字又放唔入好聽的melody<br />\n就算放得入 都只不過係一件藝術品<br />\n唔係自己真正想作的feel"},{"pid":"2c34b165ba2078135db674eeb4063ee7a00057e5","tid":372871,"uid":113224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:36:51.000Z","msg":"點解得廣東話有le個限制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇語言專家解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e7eecae187eaa65ac28c3f4a7abe3973b07606","tid":372871,"uid":135860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:39:23.000Z","msg":"其實仲有第二點 不過似乎大家唔太關心本地音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c092d0317c3f6ae109138cc7cfeb2464890a5fee","tid":372871,"uid":117184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:43:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98f4ba24095042da69cd7c8a653a42105b06f3fa","tid":372871,"uid":62550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:35:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e0bef02e0b1c2d272ad7a9458d41497dad1bef8","tid":372871,"uid":17901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:44:50.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"c08d8417b35a460cc0f3ada1a705e932c030a7fc","tid":372871,"uid":4036,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:08:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實仲有第二點 不過似乎大家唔太關心本地音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講你就講啦屌"},{"pid":"17a34b326b8d2429ed69446cb6d79394591d26c2","tid":372871,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:48:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce49e1ece974bc4cfd1598ee1c8badd94af15ed5","tid":372871,"uid":38006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:52:00.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1911192c64102a74e1c0971b7d06719ef21210","tid":372871,"uid":5574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:54:49.000Z","msg":"呢個係詞人既問題..<br />\n亦都因為香港作詞既地位高過作曲既..<br />\n<br />\n不過近年開始有改善, 啲歌開始跳得出個圈.."},{"pid":"88afcfeab0a7c51849aae5c3bbb0613e0fcf6d4c","tid":372871,"uid":135860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:22:13.000Z","msg":"一陣講第二 岩岩翻屋企"},{"pid":"7a367c0b000fbb21595ed2bda7649ea97b90394e","tid":372871,"uid":135860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:24:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個係詞人既問題..<br />\n亦都因為香港作詞既地位高過作曲既..<br />\n<br />\n不過近年開始有改善, 啲歌開始跳得出個圈..</blockquote><br />\n香港9成係先曲後詞 詞人都有責任 但曲詞人生活係同一個背景底下"},{"pid":"49c213bb8e289a4fce0d4af7f9592e041673c357","tid":372871,"uid":135860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:35:14.000Z","msg":"其二係唱片公司的限制<br />\n<br />\n我已經聽過數次「喂果首咩咩咩好hit啵 近排我想收一首」<br />\n唱片公司有2種收歌方法 <br />\n一係自己近排想要咩歌然後Sd offer比各作曲人/公司 然後由佢擇佢中意ge<br />\n二係作曲人自己作完自己交上去 問藝人or公司有無興趣<br />\n<br />\n唱片公司的人好多都係有一定年紀 好多自以為好入流 當中亦有人真係有潮流觸角<br />\n<br />\n佢地擇歌會擇岩佢地口味 or 之前hit過的歌種<br />\n而且唔會夠膽用力宣傳係新嘗試<br />\n會keep住宣傳果d超大路巷歌<br />\n<br />\n詞亦一樣 曲亦一樣 <br />\n佢地會話 我覺得你個詞/melody唔太岩<br />\n好似有點唔岩宜家人的口味<br />\n只需一句 你就可以重做<br />\n<br />\n久而久之 曲詞會知道唔同公司的口味 寫翻果種歌等佢地收 咁先唔會白做<br />\n<br />\n自己的歌會收埋 等有心人 <br />\nOr有d人已經失去自己以前寫歌的觸角<br />\n變左寫垃圾歌的音樂人 翻唔到轉頭"},{"pid":"2e345c02dd4246da259606af2e8a624894e96d56","tid":372871,"uid":135860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:40:59.000Z","msg":"大家可以討論下 我都想由大眾角度聽下 始終一個人自己諗 未必岩晒"},{"pid":"d7ad9e750d9898810f1ba22929b8c592d568814e","tid":372871,"uid":135860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:43:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實仲有第二點 不過似乎大家唔太關心本地音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講你就講啦屌</blockquote><br />\n都話大家唔太關心咖啦 早知唔晒力打"},{"pid":"135bd9df0ead6c9a8d5afd7a6b1ec42f8840988f","tid":372871,"uid":118562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f27039be040585ecc5dbd010dc2dbcb605f394e","tid":372871,"uid":50467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:58:32.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"fb029a93eea060259529f37b7110773c63665315","tid":372871,"uid":135860,"like":0,"dislike":